                            <comment id="13259615" author="anjackson" created="Mon, 23 Apr 2012 14:08:27 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I re-uploaded the patch as it had an extra format that is not necessary for this patch. Also I noticed a typo in my original issue description. The offset should be 32769, not 37633.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
